	<tr>
		<td bgcolor="#DEDACB">
	
			<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
			Simple quest item at the Clerics Guild in Felwithe, definite newbie stuff. Decaying skeletons yield chips every so often (50%ish)<BR>
Hail the bloke in the armour at the end and offer to Protect the Mother then give him chips in sets of 4, you get exp, faction and in my case every time a Strike spell that can be sold for a few silver. Mind you I'm a Tunare Cleric and it's my temple so I'm not certain everyone gets the same. The bone chips sell for about 1 silver each anyway so this isn't a money earner as a quest. Faction helps I guess.
			</font>
	
		</td>
	</tr>
	
