			<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
			They are also used for a Quest in North Qeynos.  Give 2 of them to Laushan Novashine.  You will recive faction with the Prest's of Life(followers of Rocet Nife), and he will cast ligh healing on you.<BR>
They are also a Necromancer Spell component, to summon their pets.
			</font>
	
