	<tr>
		<td bgcolor="#DEDACB">
	
			<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
			Indeed, never ever ever sell these to<BR>
merchants... in my experience necros will pay<BR>
anywhere from 1pp to 2pp for a stack of 20.<BR>
Personally, I have never dropperd below 1.5pp/20<BR>
but I have to wait longer to sell them of course.<BR>
This makes for a very easy way to bootstrap a new<BR>
character.  Bat Wings also sell for similar money<BR>
for use in the levitate spell (though bats leave<BR>
wings as loot about half as often as skeletons<BR>
leave chips, and demand seems to be higher for<BR>
chips, obviously since summoning a pet is <BR>
generally more useful than levitate)<BR>

			</font>
	
		</td>
	</tr>
	
