	<tr>
		<td bgcolor="#DEDACB">
	
			<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
			There is another quest for these in Qeynos in the paladin guild.  Tell Wolten Graf (I'm sure spelling is wrong, but phonically close) that you will crush the undead.  He will give you a chest with 6 slots in it. put 1 chip in each slot and hit the combine button.  Give it back to him and he will give exp and usually 2 rations and 2 waters.  It may be a newbie quest, but I still get pretty good exp at lvl 15.<BR>
<BR>
NOTE: Make sure you have an open slot in your inv for a chest before you talk to him.
			</font>
	
		</td>
	</tr>
	
