	<tr>
		<td bgcolor="#DEDACB">
	
			<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
			The bone chips provide a great way for Half Elf rangers to make a quick loot. I reccomend that you are level 3-5 for this. Simply go to Qeynos, hop on a boat to Erudin, where there is an abundance of decaying skeletons. Use your tracking ability to track and kill every decaying skeleton that shows up. In no time you will have stacks upon stacks of chips, which weigh close to nothing and can be taken back to Qeynos to be sold to PC's for 2pp per stack easily.<BR>
<BR>
Bayzil of Innoruuk<BR>
Follower of Tunare
